('Canon EOS 1200D Digital SLR Camera with EF-S 18-55 mm f/3.5-5.6 III Lens', '', '', '', '', '[b]Photos you\'ll be proud of[/b]\r\n\r\nShoot photos and video with a quality and character all of their own. 18-megapixel images from the EOS 1200D are packed with detail and are large enough to be printed at sizes up to A2+. Videos have a professional look and feel that looks great played back on your home HDTV.\r\n\r\n[b]Easy to use for any subject[/b]\r\n\r\nWhen you compose a photograph using the EOS 1200D the camera analyses the scene too, looking for brightness, colour and the presence of movement and faces. This information is used to set the most appropriate camera settings for the scene, whether it\'s a detail-packed landscape or fast-moving action. A built-in Feature Guide, and supporting app, help you learn more about your camera whenever you want.\r\n\r\n[b]Stay in focus[/b]\r\n\r\nKeep subjects looking sharp by placing them underneath one of the EOS 1200D\'s nine focusing points. These are spread out across the viewfinder, letting you place your subject either in the middle of the frame or off-centre, for a more interesting composition.', 'Capture the emotion of the moment, with a DSLR camera that\'s easy to use and delivers results you\'ll love.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-1', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '286.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:32:13 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'canon-eos-1200d-digital-camera', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Nikon D3200 Digital SLR Camera with 18-55mm VR Lens Kit - Black (24.2MP) 3 inch LCD', '', '', '', '', 'Boasting a resolution that`s a match for much higher priced models, while at the same time promising to make the transition from a point and shoot compact to a DSLR a breeze with a built-in Guide Mode, the Nikon D3200 looks set to tempt potential Compact System Camera purchasers back to a DSLR.\r\n\r\nThe most dramatic change from the 14.2MP D3100 (which will continue in the Nikon DSLR line-up for now) is the arrival of a 24.2MP CMOS sensor. Not only does this mean it has the second highest pixel count in the entire Nikon DSLR line-up behind the pro-spec 36.3MP full-frame D800 (eclipsing both the higher priced D5100 and D7000 as well), but offers one of the highest pixel counts ever seen on a APS-C DSLR.\r\n\r\nNikon hope the boost in resolution over the D3100 will see entry-level users wanting to crop images and refine composition safe in the knowledge that there will be limited impact on image quality.', 'As the popularity of Compact System Cameras increases with a host of new models, it`s been pretty quiet period for entry-level DSLRs over the last twelve months. This is about to change with the arrival of the Nikon D3200.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-2', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '319.00', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:43:33 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'nikon-d3200-digital-slr-camera', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Pentax K-50 DSLR Camera with DAL 18-55 mm WR Lens Kit, 3 inch LCD - Black', '', '', '', '', 'High-resolution, super-high-sensitivity shooting at ISO 51200\r\n\r\nThe K-50 features the state-of-the-art CMOS image sensor with a large image capturing area measuring 23.7mm by 15.7mm, to assure high-speed image data readout. This image sensor is coupled with PRIME M, the same high-performance imaging engine incorporated in upper-class models to deliver super-high-resolution, rich-gradation digital images with approximately 16.28 effective megapixels. The K-50 also offers super-high-sensitivity shooting at a top sensitivity of ISO 51200, allowing the photographer to handhold the camera for beautiful night-time snapshots.\r\n\r\nHigh-quality movie recording\r\n\r\nThe K-50 captures high-resolution, full HD movie clips (1920 x 1080 pixels) in the H.264 recording format, with a choice of frame rate (30, 25 or 24 frames per second). It even comes with creative image-processing tools like Custom Images and useful movie-recording features like an interval movie recording function, for the production of more personalised movies.', 'The PENTAX K-50 boasts outstanding basic specifications that rival many models, including high-speed continuous shooting at approximately six images per second, super-high-sensitivity shooting at ISO 51200, and high-precision AF with accurate tracking of moving subjects. This means that new digital SLR users and casual family photographers can enjoy high-quality digital photography with very little effort.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-3', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '399.00', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:47:06 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'pentax-k-50-dslr-camera', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('LG 43LF540V 43 inch 1080p Full HD LED TV with Freeview (2015 Model) - Silver', '', '', '', '', '[b]Metallic Design[/b]\r\n\r\nMasterfully manufactured design. A metallic material is wrapped around your television providing a cutting edge construction. This sleek housing adds a modern touch to any living room.\r\n\r\n[b]Virtual Surround[/b]\r\n\r\nMore channels, better sound. High quality software creates a surround sound effect producing virtual audio channels. Surround your senses with sound from all angles.\r\n\r\n[b]Plug and Play[/b]\r\n\r\nMultiple Digital Inputs\r\n\r\nWith mulitple inputs you can simply plug in your HDMI cable or USB and play out your entertainment, games or digital devices through your TV.', 'FULL HD 1080p provides the pinnacle of picture resolution with incredible clarity and vibrant colours. With up to five times the resolution compared to standard definition TVs and twice that of `HD-Ready` TVs, FULL HD 1080p is the only way to enjoy the full potential of Blu-ray and HD gaming.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-4', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '289.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:39:26 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'lg-43lf540v-43-inch-1080p-full-hd-led-tv', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Sony Bravia KDL40WD653 40" Full HD Smart TV with Freeview, HDD Rec and USB Playback', '', '', '', '', '[b]X-Reality PRO: a cleaner, more refined picture[/b]\r\n\r\nEnjoy high clarity, sharpness and picture quality for everything you watch. The combination of noise reduction technologies sharpen and remove noise from every scene, so the picture gleams with clear detail.\r\n\r\n[b]Full HD 1080p[/b]\r\n\r\nExperience the detail of Full HD 1080p across all your entertainment. From Blu-ray Discs to catch-up TV to smartphone photos, you can see it all in high clarity on the big screen with this Bravia TV.\r\n\r\n[b]Your smartphone on the big screen[/b]\r\n\r\nScreen mirroring lets you enjoy content and apps from your smartphone on your Sony TV. Supersize all your memories and enjoy them on the big screen with family and friends.', 'The Sony Bravia WD6 is a Full HD smart TV with a slim profile and powerful image processor that gets the most out of everything you watch. With the powerful X-Reality Pro Engine, you can enjoy amazing picture quality and improved colour, whatever the source. Even if you\'re watching non-HD content or something that you\'ve recorded on your smartphone, the engine improves the picture for a guaranteed enjoyable experience.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-5', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '379.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 19:10:56 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'sony-bravia-kdl40wd653-40-full-hd-smart-tv-with-freeview-hdd-rec-and-usb-playback', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Panasonic TX-40C300B 40 inch Full HD LED 1080p TV with Freeview HD - Black', '', '', '', '', '[b]Enhanced Image Quality[/b]\r\n\r\nPanasonic C300 Series TVs deliver high contrast high definition images with vibrant colour and enhanced contrast. Colour gradations are rich and smooth, for colourful naturalistic pictures. The viewing angle is wide, at 176 degrees, so you`ll enjoy a better picture regardless of your seating angle to the screen. The 40-, 48- and 55-inch C300 TVs are Full HD 1080p resolution. The 24- and 32-inch models are 720p HD ready.\r\n\r\n[b]Slim Unobtrusive Design[/b]\r\n\r\nPanasonic C300 Series TVs feature a narrow bezel in lustrous black to better blend with any decor as well as emphasise TV picture quality. They are all about the screen.', 'Aptly designed with a discreet narrow black bezel and unobtrusive table-top pedestal stand, the Panasonic C300 series full HD LED TVs (40, 48 and 55 inches) combine better design with enhanced TV image quality. For better high definition image quality, 200 Hz Back Light Blinking (BLB) picture technology ensures sports and action movies look crisp, while a content optimiser makes the most of every source.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-6', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '229.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:46:39 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'panasonic-tx-40c300b-40-inch-full-hd-led-1080p-tv-with-freeview-hd-black', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Lenovo Ideapad 300 15.6-Inch HD Laptop (Black) - (Intel Core i7-6500U, 8 GB RAM, 1 TB HDD, Intel HD Graphics Card, Windows 10)', '', '', '', '', '[b]Value and Versatility[/b]\r\n\r\nDesigned for deal-seekers. The ideapad 300 provides reliable performance for both productivity and leisure tasks.\r\n\r\n[b]Dolby Advanced Audio[/b]\r\n\r\nStereo speakers sound bigger and louder than ever, thanks to the experts at Dolby Laboratories.\r\n\r\nDolby technologies let you transform your ideapad 300 into a personal home theatre.\r\n\r\n[b]HD Display[/b]\r\n\r\nClearer, sharper dimension to your movies, photos, games and video chat.', 'Windows 10 Home: It is the familiar feel of Windows, only improved. The Start menu is back, better than ever. Expand it, customise it, make it yours. Work with more of the devices you care about, such as printers, cameras, and USBs. Boot up and resume quickly with technologies like InstantGo. And enjoy additional security features that help to safeguard you against device theft and malicious software.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-7', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '449.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:38:20 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'lenovo-ideapad-300-15-6-inch-hd-laptop', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('ASUS Zenbook UX305CA-FB005T 13.3 inch QHD Screen (13.3 inch QHD IPS LED, Intel Core M-6Y30, 8 GB, 128 GB, No ODD, Windows 10 (64 bit), 802.11ac, BT 4.0)', '', '', '', '', '[b]Embodying the spirit of Zen[/b]\r\n\r\nThe sophisticated design of ZenBook UX305CA is a masterpiece of craftsmanship, engineered to stand out from the crowd. It takes dozens of precisely-controlled manufacturing steps to forge each ZenBook UX305CA from a raw block of solid aluminium. The subtle and refined shape incorporates the DNA of the classic ZenBook, with an tapered wedge design that\'s practical.\r\n\r\n[b]Detailed QHD+ display[/b]\r\n\r\nThe ultra-sharp screen has an up to QHD+ resolution of 3200 by 1800 pixels and a brightness of 300 cd/m2, so it\'s always easy and comfortable to view. And with an incredible pixel density of 276 pixels per inch, images and text are always pin-sharp and ultra-detailed.', 'ZenBook UX305CA is designed to go everywhere you go. Weighing a mere 1.2 kg and just 1.23 cm thin, it\'s never a burden, always a delight. But it\'s not just a lightweight laptop: it\'s seriously powerful too, packed with the high-performance technology. With ZenBook UX305CA, you can do all the things you\'ve always wanted to do, wherever you are.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-8', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 6, '', '', '', '1000', '535.53', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 14:59:07 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'asus-zenbook-ux305ca-fb005t-13-3-inch-qhd-screen-13-3-inch-qhd-ips-led-intel-core-m-6y30-8-gb-128-gb-no-odd-windows-10-64-bit-802-11ac-bt-4-0-', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Apple MF839B/A 13-Inch MacBook Pro with Retina Display (Intel Core i5 2.7 GHz, 8 GB RAM, 128 GB SSD, OS X El Capitan) - QWERTY Keyboard', '', '', '', '', 'From the outside, Apple\'s 2015 13-inch MacBook Pro refresh is a minor one; the beautiful aluminium chassis and high resolution "Retina" display are identical to last year\'s model, and most of the changes are minor hardware specification increases. This is arguably a good thing, as the MacBook Pro is nothing short of iconic. The biggest upgrade is the addition of Force Touch, new touchpad technology (also found on the new 12in MacBook and the Apple Watch) the company hopes will change the way we interact with applications.', 'Performance-boosting upgrades and an overhauled touchpad keep the 13-inch MacBook Pro well ahead of the competition', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-9', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '896.12', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 14:57:35 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'apple-mf839b-a-13-inch-macbook-pro', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('TomTom Start 25 5 inch Sat Nav with Western European Maps and Lifetime Map Updates', '', '', '', '', '[b]Lifetime Maps[/b]\r\n\r\nAlways drive with the latest map. Get to your destination faster with Lifetime Maps.\r\n	\r\n[b]Advanced Lane Guidance[/b]\r\n\r\nClearly shows which lane to take at junctions so you don\'t miss your turning. On the most difficult highway intersections, realistic 3D representation of the junction keeps you relaxed and safe.\r\n	\r\n[b]Speed Cameras[/b]\r\n\r\nYour device will give you warning of fixed speed camera locations. It can save you money on speeding fines, helping you drive safely and relaxed.', 'Get started with a navigation system that works right from the box - the TomTom Start 25 is a great introduction to what satellite navigation can do for you, Whether you are driving familiar roads or venturing somewhere new, the TomTom Start gives you peace of mind. It`s the best device in its league, and surprisingly easy to use. See high quality maps on its larger screen, and trust it to guide you safely through complex junctions for a confident drive.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-10', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 6, '', '', '', '1000', '89.55', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 19:12:29 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'tomtom-start-25-5-inch-sat-nav-with-western-european-maps-and-lifetime-map-updates', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Garmin nuvi 57LM 5-Inch Satellite Navigation System with UK and Ireland Maps', '', '', '', '', '[b]More Information Right on Your Map[/b]\r\n\r\nThe Garmin nuvi 57LM displays your speed, the speed limit, school zones and accurate time of arrival as you drive.\r\n\r\nWith the Up Ahead feature, you can easily find places you want – like restaurants, petrol stations, cashpoints and shops – without leaving the map. Up Ahead is customisable, so you can always know the location of favourite destinations along your route.\r\n\r\nFoursquare data add millions more points of interest, so you can discover new and popular restaurants, shops and services in your area.\r\n\r\nGarmin Real Directions guide you like a friend using landmarks and traffic lights to eliminate uncertainty.\r\n\r\nDirect Access simplifies navigation to certain complicated destinations, like a shopping centre or airport.', 'Garmin nuvi 57LM has a 5 inch dual-orientation touchscreen display, preloaded street level mapping for the UK and Ireland with lifetime map updates and enhanced navigation features for a stress-free journey.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-11', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '69.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:36:13 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'garmin-nuvi-57lm-5-inch-satellite-navigation-system-with-uk-and-ireland-maps', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Noza Tec GPS Sat Nav Car GPS Navigation System with UK European Maps & Lifetime Map Updates, 7 Inch, 8GB, X7', '', '', '', '', 'CPU: MEDIA TEK MT3351 533MHZ\r\nRAM:128M\r\nTouchscreen:Yes\r\nDisplay: 7" Touch Screen\r\nChoose 2D or 3D Map: Available\r\nMemory: 8GB\r\nBluetooth: NO\r\nBattery: Built-in 1500 mA lithium battery\r\nE-book: Read txt\r\nVideo Formats: WMV, AVI, ASF\r\nAudio Formats: WMA, MP3, WAV\r\nPicture Browse:JPG, GIF, BMP, PNG\r\nCold acquisition time: Approximate 45 seconds\r\nAutoLocate: Approximately 2 minutes\r\nUpdate rate: Once per second, continuous GPS\r\nAccuracy: Position - Less than 10 meters (33 feet) 95% typical\r\nVelocity - 0.1 meters per second steady\r\nState Routes: Automatically calculated Voice\r\nPower cable: Input 12V Output 5V/1.5A\r\nMain Menu Languages 13: English, Italian, French, Spanish, German, Portuguese, Hungarian, Russian, Finnish, Polish, Romanian, Ukrainian, Slovenian\r\n\r\nPackage includes:\r\n- GPS navigation\r\n- Sunshade\r\n\r\n- Touch pen\r\n- Suction cap\r\n- Air out mount\r\n- Home charger\r\n- Car charger\r\n- USB 2.0 cable\r\n- Back bracket\r\n- Pouch\r\n- English manual', 'Preintall the latest maps of main EU countries,lifetime free updates, provide reliable guidance on the way. 7 inch super large touch screen, clear to view and convenient to operate. Free sunshade for sunny days.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-12', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '34.68', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:44:07 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'noza-tec-gps-sat-nav-car-gps-navigation-system', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Wileyfox Swift 4G Dual SIM-Free Smartphone - Black', '', '', '', '', '[b]QUAD CORE 4G LTE CAPABILITY[/b]\r\n\r\nWith a 64-bit CPU at 1.2GHz, and 4G download speeds of up to 150mbps, the Wileyfox Swift keeps your online life connected, even when you`re on the move. Dual microSIM capability gives you even more flexibility, giving you the option to have two data networks for your single handset.\r\n\r\n4G LTE connectivity, stunning picture quality from the 13MP rear camera and a quad core Snapdragon 410 processor brings this phone to the forefront of affordable smartphone technology.', 'Advanced Android-based Cyanogen OS brings the features you love while giving you the freedom to customize your mobile device. Cyanogen OS: An Open OS Built by the Users, for the Users Cyanogen backs the largest open source Android developer community in the world. They`re working to create some of the most advanced customisation, performance, and security technology available for mobile phones.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-13', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '99.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 19:14:34 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'wileyfox-swift-4g-dual-sim-free-smartphone-black', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Motorola Moto G 3rd Generation SIM-Free Smartphone 2 GB RAM/16 GB ROM', '', '', '', '', 'Powerful and affordable, the new Moto G is a smartphone you can count on. It\'s durable and water-resistant, so it won\'t let you down. And with innovative software, a 13 MP camera, and the speed of 4G LTE, it\'s ready for anything. All in one beautiful design that looks as good as it feels.', 'Powerful and affordable, the new Moto G is a smartphone you can count on. It\'s durable and water-resistant, so it won\'t let you down. And with innovative software, a 13 MP camera, and the speed of 4G LTE, it\'s ready for anything. All in one beautiful design that looks as good as it feels.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-14', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '159.39', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:41:52 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'motorola-moto-g-3rd-generation-sim-free-smartphone-2-gb-ram-16-gb-rom', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge 32GB UK SIM-Free Smartphone - Gold', '', '', '', '', '[b]Design[/b]\r\n\r\nThis phone is crafted from the high quality materials. The Edge design and AMOLED screen make the Galaxy S7 Edge an appealing phone in the market. And Samsung has made no compromises on durability, thanks to a dust and water resistant Gorilla glass build.\r\n\r\nThe curves of the Galaxy S7 Edge provide a range of practical benefits. With their its curved designs and compact dimensions, the Galaxy S7 edge fits comfortably in one hand and is the first Galaxy phone to feature capless water and dust resistance (IP68). The Edge screen provides a range of functions, including the enriched Apps edge and Task edge.\r\n\r\n[b]Performance[/b]\r\n\r\nThe brand has also enhanced all the essentials of a high quality smartphone.\r\n\r\nGalaxy S7 Edge has a large and more efficient battery than ever before. Both support wireless charging for great convenience on the go.\r\n\r\nBattery: S7 3000 mAh / S7 edge 3600 mAh\r\n\r\nCharging: S7 95 min / S7 edge 115 min\r\n\r\nWireless Charging: S7 130 min / S7 edge 150 min\r\n\r\nBig storage lets you enjoy more of your favourite music and videos. The return of the much-loved microSD slot means the Galaxy S7 Edge supports an additional 200 GB of storage', 'This is the Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge.\r\n\r\nAs the latest member of the Galaxy S family, it\'s got all the features you`ve come to know and love. Water resistance, fast charging and the return of expandable storage – it`s all there.\r\n\r\nBut the Galaxy S7 Edge is more than just a phone – it\'s the key to a Galaxy of experiences. Pair it with a Gear VR and unlock a whole world of gaming, cinema and more. The Galaxy S7 Edge\'s powerful processors take your virtual reality experience to the next level.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-15', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '523.02', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:49:24 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-32gb-uk-sim-free-smartphone-gold', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
('Ultrasport Foldable Exercise Bike With Pulse Sensor Grips', '', '', '', '', 'If you are not very sporty you can simply choose an easier resistance level. The workout doesn\'t just have a positive effect on the leg muscles but also on the back and shoulders. Those who do regular workouts can also increase their circulation and lung volume. The Ultrasport exercise bikes are also suitable for health enhancing endurance training. \r\n\r\nCycling is good for the body and spirit and is one of the most popular sports that improves your performance gently. It helps to increase stamina and endurance, protects the joints, lets you choose your own speed and not overexert yourself. The fitness device can be used when you like and the difficulty levels can be easily adjusted. This is done through the different resistance levels on the fitness bikes.This slowly increases the circulation and if nothing else, stimulates the metabolism. Beginners and more advanced cyclists can work out on the same device thanks to the adjustable settings and simply have to move the comfortable saddle to the right position before exercising.', 'The Ultrasport F-bike range of exercise bikes are the ideal solution for those who want to workout moderately. They are equipped with hand sensors to help you keep fit in your own home by constantly checking your circulation. Get noticeable results and stay motivated with the foldable workout bikes from Ultrasport. They help you to persevere and do something good for your body.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-16', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '107.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 19:13:15 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'ultrasport-foldable-exercise-bike-with-pulse-sensor-grips', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
