('V-Fit Tornado Air Rower', '', '', '', '', 'For a realistic and challenging workout in the comfort of your own home, the V-Fit tornado air power is the ideal solution to get you training like an Olympian. With a robust steel frame, an extruded aluminium rowing rail with an anatomically designed smooth action, roller mounted padded seat and a club style, speed-proportionate resistance air fan with chain drive and a contoured row handle for more intensive stroke control. \r\n\r\nThe V-Fit tornado is suited to fitness beginners and experts alike. Providing a versatile workout solution, the oversized pivoting foot plates and 2-position velcro-style toe straps help to keep your feet secure, while ensuring your movement feels as natural as possible. To help keep you motivated and focused 6-function, 2 page exercise monitor shows theoretical calorie burn, distance, speed, stroke counter, stroke rate and time modes. Requires two AA batteries. For space-saving storage, the tornado has integrated roller wheels on the front frame and can be folded to reduce the stored length. The tornado air rower supports a maximum user weight of 115 kg/253 lbs and comes with the necessary tools for home self-assembly.\r\n\r\nBox Contains\r\n\r\n1 x Rower\r\n1 x Assembly and user manual\r\n2 x Tools', 'For a realistic and challenging workout in the comfort of your own home, the V-Fit tornado air power is the ideal solution to get you training like an Olympian. With a robust steel frame, an extruded aluminium rowing rail with an anatomically designed smooth action, roller mounted padded seat and a club style, speed-proportionate resistance air fan with chain drive and a contoured row handle for more intensive stroke control.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-18', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '229.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 19:14:09 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'v-fit-tornado-air-rower', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
