('Falcon Women\'s Expression Hybrid Style City Bike - Pink/Grey, 26-Inch', '', '', '', '', 'The new Falcon expression is the ideal bike for anyone looking to ride regularly on roads, paths, tow-paths and maintained trails. Ideal as a commuter or leisure bike, the expression is equipped with front and rear mudguards to protect you from the dirt thrown up off the road, and also a rear luggage rack for stowing your belonging during your journey. \r\n\r\nThe mudguards are made from a sturdy, yet flexible plastic meaning that they are more resistant than metal mudguards if bent or knocked. The expression has a 26" tyre, so is nippy and agile and easier to transport than larger wheeled bikes, whilst the alloy wheel rims provide lightweight yet sturdy construction.The Falcon expression is ideally suited to riding on smoother trails and therefore is fitted with a super efficient trekking tyre. \r\n\r\nThe wide tyre provides great grip on the riding surface, whilst the snake-skin surface is smoother rolling for a comfortable ride. Powered by Shimano, 6 gears keep the bike lightweight and easy to use and have been designed to provide a wide ratio of gears to enable you to tackle most terrains. Front and rear V-brakes provide sturdy stopping power whilst comfort grips are soft on the hands for the longer rides. \r\n\r\nThe quill stem provides great adjustment for the handlebar height, whilst a long seat post and rail adjusters on the Falcon branded saddle, allow precise refinement of the seating position. \r\n\r\nSuitable for age 12+ years, inside leg measurement of 75-90 cms 29-35 inch', 'The new Falcon expression is the ideal bike for anyone looking to ride regularly on roads, paths, tow-paths and maintained trails. Ideal as a commuter or leisure bike, the expression is equipped with front and rear mudguards to protect you from the dirt thrown up off the road, and also a rear luggage rack for stowing your belonging during your journey.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-21', 0, 10, 'yes'