rm summer nights or during the colder months. The "Toronto" offers a broad range of possibilities for grilling and turns every barbecue into an event.', 'no', '', 0, 'mCode-32', 0, 10, 'yes', '{date}', 5, '', '', '', '1000', '134.99', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '', 0, 'Wed, 27 Jul 2016 19:11:16 +0000', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 0, 0, '', '', NULL, 'tepro-toronto-trolley-grill-barbecue-black', '', 0, 0, '0000-00-00'),
